 "conversations": [
  {
   "id": "cv_01",
   "contact_id": "c_03",
   "channel": "sms",
   "unread": 2,
   "messages": [
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Hi, I found Bronco Painting on Google. Looking to get 2 bedrooms and a hallway painted at our place in Denver. Can I get a quote?",
     "days_ago": 1,
     "hours_ago": 16
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Hi Minh, thanks for reaching out! Happy to help. What's the address, and are we doing walls, ceilings, and trim?",
     "days_ago": 1,
     "hours_ago": 14
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "1483 S Umatilla St. Walls and ceilings, trim is fine. One bedroom has wallpaper on a single wall.",
     "days_ago": 1,
     "hours_ago": 13
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Got it \u2014 we handle wallpaper removal too. We have free estimate slots later this week, want me to book one for you?",
     "days_ago": 1,
     "hours_ago": 12
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Friday after 3 works. Also, do you guys do accent walls? Thinking something dark like Iron Ore SW 7069 behind the bed.",
     "days_ago": 0,
     "hours_ago": 3
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Oh and is the estimate free?",
     "days_ago": 0,
     "hours_ago": 1
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "cv_02",
   "contact_id": "c_08",
   "channel": "sms",
   "unread": 0,
   "messages": [
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Hi, this is Grace Tran. We just bought a house on S Monaco Pkwy and want the whole interior repainted before we move in.",
     "days_ago": 3,
     "hours_ago": 10
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Congrats on the new house, Grace! We'd love to take a look. Are you available this week for a free estimate?",
     "days_ago": 3,
     "hours_ago": 9
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Yes! Mornings are best. The house is empty so any day works.",
     "days_ago": 2,
     "hours_ago": 15
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Perfect \u2014 does Thursday at 10:00 AM work? Our estimator Marisol will walk the house with you.",
     "days_ago": 2,
     "hours_ago": 14
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Thursday 10am works. See you then!",
     "days_ago": 2,
     "hours_ago": 13
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Hi Grace, quick reminder about your estimate tomorrow at 10:00 AM. Reply C to confirm.",
     "days_ago": 0,
     "hours_ago": 4
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "C \u2014 thanks!",
     "days_ago": 0,
     "hours_ago": 2
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "You're all set. See you tomorrow at 10:00!",
     "days_ago": 0,
     "hours_ago": 2
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "cv_03",
   "contact_id": "c_13",
   "channel": "email",
   "unread": 1,
   "messages": [
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Hi Marcus, attached is your exterior repaint estimate \u2014 $7,600 including power wash, scrape and prime, two coats of SW Duration on body and trim, and full caulking. Let me know if you have any questions!",
     "days_ago": 5,
     "hours_ago": 11
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Thanks. Price is a bit higher than another bid we got. What paint do they use vs yours?",
     "days_ago": 4,
     "hours_ago": 9
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Great question \u2014 we spec Sherwin-Williams Duration, a lifetime-warranty exterior paint. Lower bids usually mean SuperPaint or contractor grade, which typically needs repainting 3-4 years sooner. Our labor warranty is 3 years.",
     "days_ago": 4,
     "hours_ago": 8
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "OK, that helps. Can you break out the detached garage as a separate line item? We might phase it.",
     "days_ago": 1,
     "hours_ago": 10
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "cv_04",
   "contact_id": "c_15",
   "channel": "email",
   "unread": 0,
   "messages": [
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Hello, this is Carol with the Summit Ridge HOA board. We received your proposal for the clubhouse interior. The board meets next week \u2014 can you send a certificate of insurance and two HOA references?",
     "days_ago": 9,
     "hours_ago": 10
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Hi Carol, absolutely \u2014 COI and two HOA references attached. Happy to attend the board meeting if that would help.",
     "days_ago": 9,
     "hours_ago": 8
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "The board reviewed your proposal. We'd like to move forward pending one item: can you include the fitness room ceiling at the same price?",
     "days_ago": 3,
     "hours_ago": 14
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "We can include the fitness room ceiling if we schedule during your low-traffic window. Updated proposal attached, still at $13,200.",
     "days_ago": 2,
     "hours_ago": 10
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "That works. Our board president signs next week \u2014 please pencil us in.",
     "days_ago": 2,
     "hours_ago": 9
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "cv_05",
   "contact_id": "c_17",
   "channel": "sms",
   "unread": 0,
   "messages": [
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Hi! Following up on the cabinet quote. I'm torn on colors \u2014 thinking Naval SW 6244 for the island and Alabaster SW 7008 for the perimeter cabinets. Too trendy?",
     "days_ago": 8,
     "hours_ago": 12
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Honestly a classic combo \u2014 Naval island with Alabaster perimeter is timeless. We'd spray Emerald Urethane Trim Enamel in satin, very durable.",
     "days_ago": 8,
     "hours_ago": 11
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Ok good. My sister keeps pushing Agreeable Gray SW 7029 for the walls too.",
     "days_ago": 7,
     "hours_ago": 15
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Agreeable Gray pairs great with both. Want to book a free color consult? We bring drawdown samples so you can see them in your own light.",
     "days_ago": 7,
     "hours_ago": 14
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Yes please! Sometime later this week?",
     "days_ago": 6,
     "hours_ago": 10
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "You're booked \u2014 we'll text a confirmation. Have your countertop sample handy if you can!",
     "days_ago": 6,
     "hours_ago": 9
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "cv_06",
   "contact_id": "c_01",
   "channel": "sms",
   "unread": 1,
   "messages": [
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Hi Daniel \u2014 crew update: south and west walls are done. Weather looks iffy tomorrow morning, so we may start after lunch.",
     "days_ago": 2,
     "hours_ago": 9
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "No problem. Looks great so far.",
     "days_ago": 2,
     "hours_ago": 8
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Crew is on site \u2014 finishing trim in Snowbound SW 7004 today, then we'll do the final walkthrough with you.",
     "days_ago": 0,
     "hours_ago": 6
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Great. Quick thing \u2014 can they touch up the downspout by the garage before they wrap? Small scuff.",
     "days_ago": 0,
     "hours_ago": 2
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "cv_07",
   "contact_id": "c_22",
   "channel": "sms",
   "unread": 0,
   "messages": [
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Hi Robert, the crew wrapped up your exterior yesterday. How does everything look?",
     "days_ago": 6,
     "hours_ago": 10
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "House looks brand new. The crew was awesome and left everything spotless.",
     "days_ago": 6,
     "hours_ago": 8
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "That's what we love to hear! If you have 2 minutes, a Google review helps our small business a ton \u2014 broncopainting.example.com/review",
     "days_ago": 5,
     "hours_ago": 9
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Done \u2014 5 stars posted. We may have you back for the basement next year.",
     "days_ago": 5,
     "hours_ago": 7
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "cv_08",
   "contact_id": "c_12",
   "channel": "email",
   "unread": 0,
   "messages": [
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Hi, I manage a small portfolio for Redline Property Group. Two of our buildings on S Acoma need full exterior repaints. Can you bid from photos or do you need a site visit?",
     "days_ago": 21,
     "hours_ago": 11
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Thanks for reaching out! We'd want a quick site walk \u2014 about 45 minutes per building. We can also provide a COI naming Redline as additional insured.",
     "days_ago": 20,
     "hours_ago": 9
    },
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Site walk went well per our super. Send the proposal when ready.",
     "days_ago": 15,
     "hours_ago": 13
    },
    {
     "dir": "out",
     "text": "Proposal attached: $16,400 for both buildings \u2014 elastomeric on the stucco, Duration on siding and trim, lift rental included. Pricing valid 30 days.",
     "days_ago": 3,
     "hours_ago": 10
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "cv_09",
   "contact_id": "c_06",
   "channel": "fb",
   "unread": 1,
   "messages": [
    {
     "dir": "in",
     "text": "Hi, saw your ad \u2014 do you stain fences or just houses? Our cedar fence and deck are pretty faded.",
